    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! While it's currently in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a dedicated enthusiast. It's an affordable entry point for those who love a hands-on challenge and want to customize a ride from the ground up!",
